\end_inset

For an interval 
\begin_inset Formula $I=\left\langle a,b\right\rangle ,$
\end_inset

 where 
\begin_inset Formula $a,b\in\mathbb{R},a<b$
\end_inset

,
 the 
\begin_inset Formula $L^{2}$
\end_inset

-norm on 
