\end_inset

 be a sequence of functions in 
\begin_inset Formula $C(I)$
\end_inset

,
 where 
\begin_inset Formula $I=\left\langle a,b\right\rangle $
\end_inset

.
 This sequence is called a Cauchy sequence with respect to the 
\family roman
\series medium
